---
import TestimonialCard from '../ui/TestimonialCard.astro';
import { Image, getImage } from 'astro:assets';

import glove_img from '@assets/glove_bullet.png';
import bg_img from '@assets/main_boxing_bg_opacity.png';

const optimizedBackground = await getImage({ src: bg_img });

const testimonials= [
  {
    quote: "\"My experience training with Ken was enlightening. Having trained casually before, I had accumulated a collection of bad habits that prevented me from striking to my full potential. Ken was very knowledgeable and identified the problem almost immediately. With his tutelage, I improved my form and power within my first visit!\"",
    name: "Christopher W.",
    role: "",
    image: glove_img,
    ringColor: "ring-light-tan-dark"
  },
];
---

<section class="py-24 bg-neutral-400">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div
          class="bg-[image:var(--bg-image)] bg-cover bg-center w-full"
          style={`--bg-image: url(${optimizedBackground.src});`}
        >
      
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-justify">
        With 20 years of boxing experience and over 40 years teaching martial arts, Kanata Boxing
        offers beginner-friendly boxing classes for children, youth, and adults in Kanata and Stittsville.
        Learn to move like a butterfly and sting like a bee while improving your fitness, confidence, and
        overall well-being in a fun and supportive environment while you:
      </p>
      <br>

      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl p-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="p-4 text-justify">
            <ul>
              <li>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold">
                <Image 
                  src={glove_img}
                  alt="Boxing Glove"
                  class="inline h-12 w-auto"
                  width={128}
                  height={128}
                  decoding="async"
                  fetchpriority="high"
                /> Get Fitter</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold">
                <Image 
                  src={glove_img}
                  alt="Boxing Glove"
                  class="inline h-12 w-auto"
                  width={128}
                  height={128}
                  decoding="async"
                  fetchpriority="high"
                /> Gain Confidence</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold"><Image 
                  src={glove_img}
                  alt="Boxing Glove"
                  class="inline h-12 w-auto"
                  width={128}
                  height={128}
                  decoding="async"
                  fetchpriority="high"
                /> Reduce Stress</p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 text-justify">
            <ul>
              <li><p class="text-3xl font-bold"><Image 
                  src={glove_img}
                  alt="Boxing Glove"
                  class="inline h-12 w-auto"
                  width={128}
                  height={128}
                  decoding="async"
                  fetchpriority="high"
                /> Gain More Energy</p>
              </li>
              <li><p class="text-3xl font-bold"><Image 
                  src={glove_img}
                  alt="Boxing Glove"
                  class="inline h-12 w-auto"
                  width={128}
                  height={128}
                  decoding="async"
                  fetchpriority="high"
                /> Build Self-Esteem</p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      

      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-brown">
        Results Backed by <span class="gradient-text">Experience</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 mb-4 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full bg-light-tan-dark text-brown">
        Client Success Story
      </div>

      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl p-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8">
          {testimonials.map((testimonial) => (
            <TestimonialCard testimonial={testimonial} variant="home" />
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      <br>

      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-justify">
        The great thing about boxing is that anyone can do it, regardless of age, fitness level, or
        experience. While mastering the sweet science takes years, boxing is one of the easiest combat
        sports to begin and one where beginners often see improvements within the first couple of
        classes.
      </p>
      <br>

      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-justify">
        If you're looking to improve your fitness, build confidence, and de-stress in a fun and supportive
        environment, our beginner-friendly boxing classes offer the perfect place to start. Proudly
        serving Kanata and Stittsville, we're the area's only stand-alone boxing program.
      </p>
      <br>

      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-justify">
        Our Children's Boxing Classes are all about having fun while developing healthy exercise
        habits. Through engaging and energetic classes, children improve their hand-eye coordination,
        balance, agility, concentration, confidence, and self-esteem. The discipline and focus they
        develop in class often carry over into improved performance at school and in everyday life!
      </p>
      <br>
      
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-justify">
        Our Youth Boxing Classes are all about giving them the “action” this age group needs. Getting
        them busy with a fun, exciting activity that will make them look forward to the next session.
        Getting them to burn off excess energy and frustration while getting stronger, fitter and more
        agile in our dynamic cutting-edge workout!!
      </p>
      <br>
      
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-justify">
        Our Adult Boxing Classes are designed to help adults in Kanata and Stittsville stay active,
        improve fitness, and build confidence where it's all about regaining your youth and staying
        active for years to come, enabling you to enrich your lifestyle. Don't worry if you're not in shape,
        that's what training in our dynamic boxing program is all about getting back to action and feeling
        fitter in no time. Thinking of it this quote by Dr. Kenneth Cooper: “you don't stop working out
        because you get old, you get old when you stop working out.” Think of it this way, if you can't
        squat, run or jump when you're 40, what will you be like when you're 60? Already there… with
        over 20 years boxing and working in the fitness field that's what were here for…We become
        invested in your success!
      </p>
      <br>
      
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-justify">
        We don't believe one schedule fits everyone. That's why we work around your availability.
        Whether you prefer small group training (capped at just four participants) or one-on-one
        coaching, your progress is personally monitored every step of the way.
      </p>
      

    </div>
    </div>

    
  </div>
</section>
